About Jason Cadwell


Jason was born in Corvallis grew up in Sweet Home, and graduated from Sweet Home High School. After attending Linn Benton Community College and Oregon State University, he worked for Hewlett Packard. Jason found real estate to be his passion and was licensed in 2001. He worked for The Prudential Real Estate Professionals, then Re/Max Integrity, and in June of 2013 he started his own company - Cadwell Realty Group.
